        "props": {
          "heading": "WHAT WE DO",
          "subheading": "From a lash nap to a fashion-forward haircut, we invite you to let us make you beautiful. The ultimate salon experience begins when you walk through our doors. Our customer service and artistically trained professionals will provide you with the relaxation and style that you need, making us the leader in salon services including lash extensions, special-event hair styling (bridal updos) & makeup.",
