            {
              "description": "Mega Volume Lashes are the boldest, fullest style of lash extensions—designed for maximum drama and density.",
              "imageUrl": "https://cdn.heyiris.io/cloud-files/1781757306_mb-volume-real.jpg",
              "heading": "Mega Volume Lashes",
              "title": "Mega Volume Lashes"
            },
            {
              "description": "Bridal upstyle is an elegant, fully styled hairstyle where the hair is lifted and secured up off the shoulders—designed to last all day while complementing your dress, face shape, and overall bridal look.",
              "imageUrl": "https://cdn.heyiris.io/cloud-files/1781758134_mb-bridal-real.jpg",
              "heading": "Bridal Upstyle",
              "title": "Bridal Upstyle"
            },
            {
              "description": "A lash lift is a low-maintenance treatment that enhances your natural lashes by lifting and curling them from the root—giving the appearance of longer, fuller lashes without extensions.",
